title: 'We can write an underscore _ in place of values which we expect the type checker to fill in, so the above definition could also be written as:'
pid: dbfad0f8-b3f4-40ac-bc7b-e857ae287567
body: |2-
  This example uses the [[id:732d2202-44d1-4fbf-867a-fc04290ef9a0][dependent pair syntactic sugar]].

  vec : (n : Nat ** Vect n Int)
  vec = (_ ** [3, 4])
